Preferred Rewards
Preferred Rewards gives you benefits and rewards across your eligible Bank of America® banking and Merrill Edge® investment accounts. When you are enrolled in the program, you will increase your BankAmericard Travel Rewards® 10% customer points bonus to a 25%-75% rewards bonus on every purchase.
